      <title>泰国向老年人发放 8.9 亿美元以促进经济发展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/thailand-hands-out-890-million-to-elderly-in-boost-for-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国周一向老年人发放了约 300 亿泰铢（8.9 亿美元）补助，这是政府为解决高生活成本和刺激该国低迷经济而推出的计划的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/thailand-hands-out-890-million-to-elderly-in-boost-for-economy</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 05:29:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内阁对里夫斯的英国机场计划能否带来推动作用仍存疑虑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/cabinet-doubts-linger-over-boost-from-reeves-uk-airport-plan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国内阁大臣们正在质疑伦敦希思罗机场、盖特威克机场和卢顿机场的扩建计划是否能产生预期的增长效应，因为政府内部因财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯的增长计划而产生紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/cabinet-doubts-linger-over-boost-from-reeves-uk-airport-plan</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
