      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/norway-s-government-faces-crunch-week-in-row-over-eu-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[距离西欧最大能源出口国挪威下次大选仅剩七个月，该国执政联盟岌岌可危。]]></description>
