      <title>卢旺达支持的叛军宣称控制战略要地刚果城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/rwanda-backed-rebels-claim-control-of-strategic-congolese-city</link>
      <description><![CDATA[与卢旺达结盟的叛军组织称其占领了刚果民主共和国东部一个重要的贸易枢纽，这增加了这两个中非国家爆发全面战争的可能性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/rwanda-backed-rebels-claim-control-of-strategic-congolese-city</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 04:55:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
