    <item>
      <title>特朗普暂缓对哥伦比亚征收 25% 关税，就移民问题达成协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-to-hold-off-on-colombia-tariffs-white-house-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在全球市场震动的几个小时内，美国总统唐纳德·特朗普宣布对哥伦比亚征收全面关税，然后在就遣返被驱逐移民达成协议后突然撤回威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/us-to-hold-off-on-colombia-tariffs-white-house-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 03:20:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普上任第二周将考验他对国会的影响力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-s-second-week-in-office-tests-his-influence-over-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统刚刚用记号笔签发了一系列行政命令，本周他开始拉拢、哄骗和强迫立法部门的成员支持他的议程和内阁人选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-27/trump-s-second-week-in-office-tests-his-influence-over-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 27 Jan 2025 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>哥伦比亚投资者准备应对特朗普关税导致的比索暴跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/colombia-investors-brace-for-peso-slump-on-trump-tariffs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在哥伦比亚与美国就驱逐移民问题产生的争端引发了唐纳德·特朗普总统短暂的关税威胁之后，哥伦比亚交易员们正准备迎接周一的动荡交易日。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-26/colombia-investors-brace-for-peso-slump-on-trump-tariffs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 22:30:43 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>刚果卢旺达支持的叛军称他们占领了关键城市</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/congo-severs-ties-with-rwanda-as-rebels-close-in-on-goma-displacing-thousands</link>
      <description><![CDATA[刚果戈马（美联社）——周一凌晨，卢旺达支持的叛军声称已占领刚果东部最大城市戈马，联合国称戈马 200 万居民陷入大规模恐慌，刚果政府则称叛军的推进是“宣战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/congo-severs-ties-with-rwanda-as-rebels-close-in-on-goma-displacing-thousands</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 10:26:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>雨水帮助加州消防员，但带来有毒灰烬的风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/rain-finally-falling-in-southern-california-helps-firefighters-but-creates-risk-of-toxic-ash-runoff</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洛杉矶（美联社）——周日，南加州部分地区迎来降雨，预计零星阵雨将持续一夜，这增加了洛杉矶地区野火烧焦地区出现有毒灰烬径流的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-01-26/rain-finally-falling-in-southern-california-helps-firefighters-but-creates-risk-of-toxic-ash-runoff</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 05:18:00 GMT</pubDate>
